his songs, were characteristics which we all admired and which will
be part of his legacy.
   ``His songs have become woven into the very fabric of American
society, touching the lives of generations of Americans,'' the
president said.
   ``Barbara and I extend our sympathies to his family and join the
American people in mourning the loss of this great American.''
